

1. endpoint url/uri
    - ip address / hostname
    - port
    - protocol (jdbc, http, https ....)

    Ex. mysql-server:3306
        http://myapplication:8080

2. Authentication
   - username/password
   - username/token
   - token
   - LDAP, IAM


Simple Example
 For MYSQL DB
     - HOST
     - PORT
     - USERNAME
     - PASSWORD
     - DATABASE


Development Environment : DB for dev  env will be different
QA Environment : DB for qa  env will be different
Production Environment : prod for dev  env will be different


